Learn Technical Analysis
June 11-12, 2002 

In today's volatile energy markets, those who are able to make objective buy and sell decisions can make significant profits and greatly improve cash flow for themselves or their companies. 

Charting Basics, Types of Charts, Support and Resistance
When to Buy or Sell
When to Exit Based on Signals 
How to Exit Based on Stops 
Chart Patterns and Forecasting Basics 
Statistical Hedging

 

